<font color=#FFFF00>Biarkan saja meskipun dia
memprovokasimu.</font>

356
00:23:02,410 --> 00:23:04,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Liburan musim panas sebentar lagi,
dan kita akan lulus tak lama setelahnya.</font>

357
00:23:05,740 --> 00:23:07,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku jadi begini karena dia memukul
Young Jun.</font>

358
00:23:08,910 --> 00:23:11,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, memikirkan ini
membuatku mau marah.</font>

359
00:23:11,610 --> 00:23:12,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Dasar kunyuk sialan.</font>

360
00:23:13,710 --> 00:23:15,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku kesal sekali.</font>

361
00:23:15,380 --> 00:23:18,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus melakukan sesuatu.
Aku akan menarik rambutnya..</font>

362
00:23:18,440 --> 00:23:20,510
<font color=#FFFF00>dan menendangnya dengan keras
sampai dia sadar.</font>

363
00:23:21,440 --> 00:23:23,280
<font color=#FFFF00>- Akan kuberi si kunyuk itu pelajaran..
- Hei.</font>

364
00:23:28,410 --> 00:23:31,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah, aku tidak akan bertengkar.
Aku akan menghindarinya.</font>

365
00:23:32,080 --> 00:23:33,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau serius?</font>

366
00:23:33,740 --> 00:23:35,440
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ya.
- Berjanjilah padaku.</font>

367
00:23:36,480 --> 00:23:37,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

368
00:24:04,610 --> 00:24:06,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan bolos kelas seni hari ini.</font>

369
00:24:06,410 --> 00:24:07,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau mau pergi kerja
paruh waktu?</font>

370
00:24:07,710 --> 00:24:08,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mana bisa bolos.</font>

371
00:24:30,380 --> 00:24:31,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Berapa harganya ini?</font>

372
00:24:33,410 --> 00:24:34,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku benar-benar minta
maaf.</font>

373
00:24:35,110 --> 00:24:36,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bilang ada urusan keluarga.
Mau bagaimana lagi.</font>

374
00:24:37,240 --> 00:24:38,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergilah.</font>

375
00:24:38,710 --> 00:24:39,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

376
00:24:40,010 --> 00:24:42,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan bekerja dua kali
lebih keras besok.</font>

377
00:24:42,710 --> 00:24:45,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah. Sana.</font>

378
00:24:45,880 --> 00:24:47,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sebaiknya menyuruh Deok Ho
ke sini.</font>

379
00:24:47,740 --> 00:24:48,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Bos.</font>

380
00:24:49,210 --> 00:24:51,210
<font color=#FFFF00>- Boleh aku pinjam teleponnya?
- Tentu.</font>

381
00:25:10,540 --> 00:25:11,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo?</font>

382
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:12,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei.</font>

383
00:25:13,710 --> 00:25:14,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini aku.</font>

384
00:25:15,810 --> 00:25:16,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau Hae Sung?</font>

385
00:25:17,610 --> 00:25:19,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bolos kerja hari ini.</font>

386
00:25:19,310 --> 00:25:20,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan ke tempatmu sekarang.</font>

387
00:25:20,810 --> 00:25:23,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Kau mau datang sekarang?</font>

388
00:25:25,980 --> 00:25:26,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa?</font>

389
00:25:27,640 --> 00:25:28,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, mau datang saja.</font>

390
00:25:29,010 --> 00:25:30,510
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aku berangkat sekarang.
- Hei, tunggu.</font>

391
00:25:30,780 --> 00:25:32,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, tolong aku.</font>

392
00:25:32,480 --> 00:25:33,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku..</font>

393
00:25:34,440 --> 00:25:38,380
<font color=#FFFF00>aku meninggalkan dompetku
di ruang seni sekolah.</font>

394
00:25:38,810 --> 00:25:40,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa kau ambilkan itu untukku?</font>

395
00:25:40,480 --> 00:25:42,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau 'kan bisa datang pagi besok
dan mengambilnya.</font>

396
00:25:42,510 --> 00:25:45,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku butuh dompetku sebelum
berangkat sekolah besok.</font>

397
00:25:46,010 --> 00:25:48,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Lagi pula kau 'kan searah.</font>

398
00:25:49,810 --> 00:25:50,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah. Akan kuambilkan.</font>

399
00:25:51,280 --> 00:25:52,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Tempat dudukmu di ruang seni..</font>

400
00:25:53,910 --> 00:25:54,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Di barisan kiri 'kan?</font>

401
00:25:54,980 --> 00:25:57,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Setelah itu, mari bertemu di tempatmu.</font>

402
00:25:57,910 --> 00:25:59,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Bawa dompetku ke tempatmu.</font>

403
00:25:59,910 --> 00:26:01,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai jumpa. Dah.</font>

404
00:26:01,210 --> 00:26:02,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

405
00:26:08,010 --> 00:26:10,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Jung Won, apa Hae Sung
sedang di jalan menuju ke sini?</font>

406
00:26:10,080 --> 00:26:12,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Gambarku masih belum selesai.</font>

407
00:26:12,380 --> 00:26:15,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan cemas, kita punya banyak waktu kok.
Kita pasti bisa menyelesaikannya.</font>

408
00:26:16,240 --> 00:26:17,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Cepatlah.</font>

409
00:26:39,110 --> 00:26:41,240
<font color=#FFFF00>(14 June, 2005, Berawan)</font>

410
00:26:51,310 --> 00:26:52,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai juga.</font>

411
00:27:12,680 --> 00:27:14,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, Jung Won.</font>

412
00:27:15,280 --> 00:27:17,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia meninggalkan dompetnya entah di mana
dan dia kira itu di sini.</font>

413
00:27:20,210 --> 00:27:21,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begini mana bisa
dia tanpa aku.</font>

414
00:27:40,280 --> 00:27:41,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang Jung Chul.</font>

415
00:27:43,440 --> 00:27:45,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Jung Chul, bangunlah. Jung Chul!</font>

416
00:27:59,310 --> 00:28:02,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan panggil ambulan.
Tunggu di sini sebentar.</font>

417
00:28:02,080 --> 00:28:03,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan segera kembali, mengerti?</font>

418
00:28:04,310 --> 00:28:05,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus tetap sadar.</font>

419
00:29:04,240 --> 00:29:06,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Hae Sung harusnya sudah sampai.
Ke mana dia?</font>

420
00:29:06,740 --> 00:29:09,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia akan segera sampai.
Ayo matikan lampu.</font>

421
00:29:09,740 --> 00:29:10,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Kedengarannya seru.</font>

422
00:29:12,780 --> 00:29:14,080
<font color=#FFFF00>- Kumatikan lampunya, ya.
- Baiklah.</font>

423
00:29:27,240 --> 00:29:28,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Diamlah. Dia sudah sampai.</font>

424
00:29:28,540 --> 00:29:29,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sampai.</font>

425
00:29:33,410 --> 00:29:35,310
<font color=#FFFF00>- Selamat ulang tahun!
- Selamat ulang tahun!</font>

426
00:29:57,540 --> 00:30:00,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada orang, kenapa pintunya
terbuka sendiri?</font>

427
00:30:01,380 --> 00:30:03,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasti karena angin.</font>

428
00:30:06,610 --> 00:30:09,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Hari itu, Hae Sung meninggal.</font>

429
00:30:12,410 --> 00:30:15,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan baru menyadari..</font>

430
00:30:17,080 --> 00:30:20,210
<font color=#FFFF00>bukan angin yang membuka
pintunya malam itu.</font>

431
00:30:20,810 --> 00:30:22,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Mungkin saja itu Hae Sung.</font>

432
